      "Text": "Security update for libxml2",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for libxml2 fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2026-6732: crafted XSD-validated document can cause a denial of service (bsc#1262719).\n- CVE-2026-11979: stack-based buffer overflows in the `xmlcatalog` utility when running in `--shell` mode (bsc#1269790).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
